<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>How It Works — Vinculum Protocol</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Lock any of 1001 approved assets on its native chain. Earn $VCLM on Base. Simple, transparent, and earned through commitment." />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;1,300&family=DM+Sans:wght@200;300;400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    :root {
      --white: #fafaf8;
      --off-white: #f4f3ef;
      --black: #0a0a0a;
      --mid: #6b6b65;
    }
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body {
      background: var(--white);
      color: var(--black);
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 300;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }
    nav {
      position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
      background: rgba(250,250,248,0.95);
      backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
    }
    .nav-logo {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-weight: 300; font-size: 1.1rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--black); text-decoration: none;
    }
    .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 2rem; list-style: none; }
    .nav-links a {
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--black); opacity: 0.75; text-decoration: none;
    }
    .section {
      padding: 6rem 2rem;
      max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto;
    }
    h1 {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-weight: 300; font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 3.2rem);
      line-height: 1.15; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .step {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 80px 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
      align-items: start;
    }
    .step-number {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 3.2rem;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
      line-height: 1;
    }
    .step-content h3 {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-weight: 300;
      font-size: 1.45rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
    }
    footer {
      background: var(--white);
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
      padding: 3rem 2rem;
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      color: var(--mid);
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 2rem;
    }
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      nav .nav-links { display: none; }
      .section { padding: 4rem 1.5rem; }
      .step { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- Navigation -->
  <nav>
    <a href="index.html" class="nav-logo">Vinculum</a>
    <ul class="nav-links">
      <li><a href="index.html#protocol">Protocol</a></li>
      <li><a href="index.html#tokens">Tokens</a></li>
      <li><a href="assets.html">Assets</a></li>
      <li><a href="index.html#governance">Governance</a></li>
      <li><a href="index.html#roadmap">Roadmap</a></li>
      <li><a href="demo/">Demo</a></li>
    </ul>
  </nav>

  <div class="section" style="padding-top: 8rem;">
    <h1>How It Works</h1>
    <p style="max-width: 680px; font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--mid);">
      Lock any of 1001 approved assets on its native chain. Earn $VCLM on Base. 
      Your asset stays where it is. Your reward is earned through commitment.
    </p>

    <!-- Step 1 -->
    <div class="step" style="margin-top: 4rem;">
      <div class="step-number">01</div>
      <div class="step-content">
        <h3>Choose your asset and duration</h3>
        <p>Select from 1001 approved tokens across many blockchains. Choose how long you want to commit (minimum 7 days). All assets earn at the same rate — dollar for dollar, with no multipliers.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Step 2 -->
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-number">02</div>
      <div class="step-content">
        <h3>Lock on the native chain</h3>
        <p>Your asset is locked directly on its home chain by the protocol’s spoke vault contract. It never leaves that chain. A 5% protocol fee is taken at the moment of lock. The remaining 95% is returned to you when the lock matures.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Step 3 -->
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-number">03</div>
      <div class="step-content">
        <h3>Earn $VCLM on Base</h3>
        <p>Once the lock is recorded locally on the native chain, the vault sends a single cross-chain message to Base requesting the mint of your $VCLM. The $VCLM is minted instantly and sent to your wallet. Your reward is calculated on the full committed amount.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div style="margin-top: 4rem; padding-top: 3rem; border-top: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.08);">
      <h3 style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-weight: 300; font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Important Details</h3>
      <ul style="font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--mid); line-height: 1.9; padding-left: 1.2rem;">
        <li>Your asset stays on its native chain at all times — it is never bridged or moved.</li>
        <li>$VCLM is minted on Base the moment your commitment is confirmed.</li>
        <li>The 5% fee is taken from the committed asset, but your $VCLM reward is based on the full amount before the fee.</li>
        <li>Axelar is used only to securely deliver the mint instruction to Base. It plays no role in locking or custody of your asset.</li>
        <li>Every $VCLM that exists is earned through real commitment.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <footer>
    <div>
      <strong>Vinculum Protocol</strong><br>
      <span style="font-size: 0.75rem;">No presale • No premine • Pure commitment</span>
    </div>
    <div style="text-align: right; font-size: 0.75rem;">
      © 2026 Vinculum Protocol DAO LLC<br>
      <a href="https://twitter.com/VinculumDefi" style="color: var(--mid); text-decoration: none;">@VinculumDefi</a>
    </div>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>